title: Prospect Park
description: Prospect Park is a public park in the New York City borough of Brooklyn. It is located between the neighborhoods of Park Slope, Prospect Heights, Windsor Terrace, and Flatlng. The park is bounded by Prospect Park West, 9th Street, Prospect Park Southwest, and 15th Street.

title: Desert Island
description: Desert Island is a record store located in the East Village neighborhood of Manhattan, New York City. It is located at 540 East 5th Street, between Avenues A and B.

title: Mast Books
description: Mast Books is a bookstore in New York City. It is located at 63 East 4th Street in the East Village neighborhood of Manhattan. The store specializes in rare and out-of-print books, and is known for its collection of books on art, photography, and architecture.
